title: Vaults of Terra - (Space Marine) Chapters - Raven Guard - History
description:
From the Vaults of Terra comes the history of the Raven Guard Space Marine chapter in the ongoing effort to reveal the history of the Space Marines.

Voting is still pen for Space Marine chapters so do keep voting.
